OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPeople to be paid again for
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fusing less electricity     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Discounts for households to use less   
OL,6, electricity at peak times will be      
OL,7, offered again on Tuesday as part of a  
OL,8, scheme to avoid blackouts.             
OL,10,FNational Grid's Demand Flexibility     
OL,11,FService will be offered to eligible    
OL,12,Fhouseholds between 16:30 and 18:00 GMT.
OL,14,FThose who have signed up will get      
OL,15,Fdiscounts on their bills if they do    
OL,16,Fthings like delay using their oven.    
OL,18,FThe service ran for the first time on  
OL,19,FMonday from 17:00 to 18:00 GMT,        
OL,20,Falthough several trials have been held.
